Step 1) Toggle LoftJump
Step 2) Hold your feather in your hand
Step 3) Reduce fall damage!

Command reference:
/loftjump (alias /lj)
/loftjump toggle [player] (alias /lj t) - toggle a player's use
/loftjump free [player] (alias /lj f) - toggle item consumption on a player
/loftjump check [world] (alias /lj c) - check the file configuration for a world
/loftjump reload - reload the file configuration

Permissions nodes:
loftjump.use 
loftjump.free
loftjump.free.others
loftjump.toggle
loftjump.toggle.others
loftjump.check
loftjump.check.others
loftjump.reload

If Permissions is not detected, then these default to checking OP status.